.TH "nvme_init_get_features" 9 "nvme_init_get_features" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_features \- Initialize passthru command for Get Features
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_features
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u8 fid "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_get_features_sel sel "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "fid" 12
Feature identifier, see \fIenum nvme_features_id\fP
.IP "sel" 12
Select which type of attribute to return,
see \fIenum nvme_get_features_sel\fP
